function br()
        pos = torso.CFrame*cfn(0,5,0)
       
        torso.Anchored = true
        ef = T.P(1,1,1,'Magenta',.5,false,true) T.FM(ef,'sphere',10,30,10)
        T.C(function() while wait(.2) and torso.Anchored do
                _,gp = FindGround(l(torso,0,-5,0).p,30,{char,m})
                if gp then
                        local wave = T.P(1,1,1,'White',0,false,true) local msh = T.FM(wave,'ring',5,5,1)
                        wave.CFrame = cfn(gp)*ang(math.pi/2,0,0)
                        T.C(function()
                                for i = 0,1,.05 do
                                        msh.Scale = v3n(70*i,70*i,1)
                                        wave.Transparency = i
                                        wait()
                                end
                                wave:Destroy()
                        end)
                end end
                end)
 
        for i = 1,360*10,60 do
                torso.CFrame = (pos*ang(-math.pi/2,md(i),0))*cfn(0,i/30,0)
                ef.CFrame = l(torso,0,-7,0)
                wait()
        end
        ef:Destroy()
        torso.Anchored = false
        char:MakeJoints()
end
